@startuml technology-sequence-event-persistence-snapshot-policy-v1
title Event Persistence and Snapshot Policy (Operational Scenario)

participant "LangGraph Orchestrator\nAPP-016" as APP_016
database "EventStore\nAPP-001" as APP_001

APP_016 -> APP_001: append_event(event_type, event_id, correlation_id)
APP_016 -> APP_001: should_create_periodic_snapshot()

alt periodic threshold reached
  APP_016 -> APP_001: create_snapshot(trigger="periodic")
else no periodic snapshot due
  APP_001 --> APP_016: no_snapshot_required()
end

opt situative checkpoint trigger
  APP_016 -> APP_001: create_snapshot(trigger in {"engagement.started","gate.evaluated","sprint.close"})
end

note right of APP_001
Scenario scope: persistence and snapshot policy only.
Replay hydration and observability reads are modeled separately.
end note
@enduml
